        "id": "CHUNK_01",
        "title": "Deployment & Failover Architecture",
        "text": "The retrieval architecture utilizes a multi-cluster failover strategy. In the event of a latency spike exceeding 400ms, the agentic runtime will automatically fallback to the regional cold-storage indices. This ensures high-availability operations for all critical client endpoints.",
